        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When the card instructs you to \u201cuse\u201d a token, you must"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "discard"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/d/discard",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/D/discard"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "one of those tokens to use the following ability. If you no longer have tokens to discard, you cannot resolve effects that require you to use a token."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "ul",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "li",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When you resolve an effect that uses multiple tokens (such as a \"Use X\" effect), effects that trigger on \"using a token\" resolve once for each token used."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
